title: #92Noon at Vikings Training Camp!
description: Tuesday show features Florio to start, then VEN's Tatum Everett for a couple segments, then it's WR Adam Thielen and ST coordinator Ryan Ficken midway thru...final hour with Lavelle on the perch, then Mike Zimmer/Kirk Cousins pressers to close!
